{"id": "1243595249889312859", "channel_id": "1243595249889312859", "type": 0, "author_id": "453161298931482626", "author_name": "nightmorals", "author_bot": false, "content": "ipad mini 6，os 17.4.1\n這台性能應該還不算過時吧？玩什麼都很正常，多人對戰的、3D的遊戲都沒問題，效能也能調挺高的玩；就這遊戲玩十分鐘就開始全方位的卡頓，主畫面也卡、戰鬥中也卡、各種界面卡卡卡，一卡左下角就開始飆2200 ms之類的爆ping提示，明明網路狀況好得不得了。就算特效全開最低+限制30幀也一點用都沒有，關卡中甚至能卡到連牌都拖不出去，極度影響遊戲體驗。每次都必須重開才能正常，然而維持不到10分鐘又會開始卡。\n\n拜託處理一下吧⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2024-05-24T16:03:32.456000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1243595249889312859", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」能不能優化一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1243599933962195005", "channel_id": "1243595249889312859", "type": 0, "author_id": "74363790983954432", "author_name": "valse.zhou", "author_bot": false, "content": "+1 ipad 8th os 17.5.1（最新） 目前也差不多情況，所有特效能低的最低，能關的都關，不過我開的60幀。時不時會出現畫面卡住，以及最嚴重的直接整個遊戲”跳出“問題以及“黑屏”問題（須重啟遊戲後才能繼續遊玩），希望官方能優化下，或者要不出個PC版也好。。謝", "timestamp": "2024-05-24T16:22:09.226000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-25T07:39:45.791000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1243595249889312859", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」能不能優化一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1243616703477321878", "channel_id": "1243616703477321878", "type": 0, "author_id": "1239915909364318208", "author_name": "cq_zheng", "author_bot": false, "content": "1、在哪里可以查看融灾禁区的boss机制呢，只能靠经验或者通过打完boss关明白。\n\n2、感觉这个命轮的描述我不是很清楚，这个最后的描述“「打击」将1张「灵感」置入手中，当回合最多触发1次。” 中的「打击」\n\n2.1、「打击」是指所有队伍中任意唤醒体还是装配该命轮的唤醒体？\n2.2、这个「打击」是指打出「打击」才会获得灵感还是手牌中有「打击」就可以获得灵感呢？", "timestamp": "2024-05-24T17:28:47.390000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1243616703733043291", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-01-19-42-779_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 116506, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243616703477321878/1243616703733043291/Screenshot_2024-05-25-01-19-42-779_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69ccad0f&is=69cb5b8f&hm=62ddc2cd1c818947714404278c9b2e98a253df722c8e0a4cba6883972deac948&"}, {"id": "1243616704031096832", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-01-19-25-760_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 199008, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243616703477321878/1243616704031096832/Screenshot_2024-05-25-01-19-25-760_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69ccad0f&is=69cb5b8f&hm=d415f487b258e95eeb8a4ff279e7f9ac5e7c36f10a07c3d2de5489b9a825bd41&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1243616703477321878", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅ 「已回答」有两个小疑问", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
